  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/02872248e5368c71021df9bbc1db4876.poster.avif?t=1760545887\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/02872248e5368c71021df9bbc1db4876.webm?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/02872248e5368c71021df9bbc1db4876.mp4?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/9f90b7b2df63e3839edd6a14bd9871c8.avif?t=1760545887\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>Your world is under siege! Dark forces have found a way to tap into your portal network putting the village in ultimate peril! Roam the land in search of daemons powerful enough to battle the eldritch invaders and defend your village! Set out to an unknown realm in hopes of closing <i>the last portal</i>!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/3bcb5c1ec6e9b5b3f8709fda2cadadda.avif?t=1760545887\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>Build a powerful deck with the daemons you seal on the way! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/b505be8648b8f8b940863e75be1d0783.poster.avif?t=1760545887\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/b505be8648b8f8b940863e75be1d0783.webm?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/b505be8648b8f8b940863e75be1d0783.mp4?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/aed1fd6a217749d0983d8b46ef1d8b79.avif?t=1760545887\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>Navigate a hex grid over-world and choose a strategic path! Explore diverse biomes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/ff407485219e63012dd78e19ff7f2675.poster.avif?t=1760545887\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/ff407485219e63012dd78e19ff7f2675.webm?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/ff407485219e63012dd78e19ff7f2675.mp4?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/2d9ba7ce3f5a78e505d3ffa861e28958.poster.avif?t=1760545887\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/2d9ba7ce3f5a78e505d3ffa861e28958.webm?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/2d9ba7ce3f5a78e505d3ffa861e28958.mp4?t=1760545887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2632650/extras/1b152f74ec925cf14b1d8ecc73b1a97d.avif?t=1760545887\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br>Earn XP after each run! Spent your XP in a roguelite upgrade system!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video cl